'''安德魯·米高·"安迪"·朗拿根'''（{{lang-en|'''Andrew Michael Andy Lonergan'''}}，{{bd|1983年|10月19日|catIdx=Lonergan, Andrew}}），是一名[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，司職[[門將|門將]]<ref name=autogenerated1>{{en}}[http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20110725/lonergan-joins-united_2247585_2401481 Leeds United | News | News | News | LONERGAN JOINS UNITED<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20110725/lonergan-joins-united_2247585_2401481 |date=20160914155117 }}</ref>。現效力於[[英超|英超]]俱乐部[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]，曾經是[[英格蘭20歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U20]]球員，同時亦有資格代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]踼球<ref name=autogenerated3>{{en}}[http://www.lep.co.uk/sport/football/lonergan_could_play_for_republic_1_93761 Lonergan could play for Republic - Football - lep.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lep.co.uk/sport/football/lonergan_could_play_for_republic_1_93761 |date=20101031101222 }}</ref>。他是2008/09和2009/10球季普雷斯頓的年度最佳球員<ref name=autogenerated8>{{en}}[http://www.pnefcpics.com/football_preston_north_end_player_of_the_year_awards/print/1503055.html Football - Preston North End Player of the Year Awards. Preston North End, Player of the Year Awards 2009, Player of the Year Awards. Preston North End<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pnefcpics.com/football_preston_north_end_player_of_the_year_awards/print/1503055.html |date=20120326140629 }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated7>{{en}}[http://www.pnefcpics.com/football_preston_north_end_feature_deepdale_09_10_28_4_10_andy_lonergan_preston_north_end_receives_the_player_of_the_year_award_mandatory_credit_action_images_/print/3169937.html Football - Preston North End Feature - Deepdale - 09/10 - 28/4/10. Andy Lonergan - Preston North End receives the player of the year award. Mandatory Credit: Action Images / E...<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pnefcpics.com/football_preston_north_end_feature_deepdale_09_10_28_4_10_andy_lonergan_preston_north_end_receives_the_player_of_the_year_award_mandatory_credit_action_images_/print/3169937.html |date=20120326140640 }}</ref>。

==球會==
===普雷斯頓===
身為普雷斯頓支持者的朗拿根，時任領隊[[大衛·莫耶斯|莫耶斯]]在他16歲時，派遣他出戰作客[[高雲地利足球會|高雲地利]]的[[英格蘭聯賽盃|聯賽盃]]賽事而首次代表普雷斯頓上陣。其後，他先後被外借至[[達寧頓足球會|達寧頓]]和[[黑池足球會|黑池]]<ref name=autogenerated4>{{en}}[http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~340964,00.html Blackpool | News | Latest News | Latest News | We Speak To Andrew Lonergan<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.blackpoolfc.co.uk/page/NewsDetail/0,,10432~340964,00.html |date=20120902124753 }}</ref>。

{{Link-en|奇治·布朗|Craig Brown (footballer, born 1940)|布朗}}接替轉投[[愛華頓足球會|愛華頓]]的莫耶斯出任普雷斯頓領隊，朗拿根對自己的前境感到樂觀，他在2002/03球季獲提升上-{一}-隊。2003/04球季，原正選門將{{Link-en|乔纳森·古尔德|Jonathan Gould|古尔德}}受傷，朗拿根臨危受命出戰聯賽對[[西布朗足球會|西布朗]]的賽事，其後他穩坐正選位置直至球季結束。

2004年10月2日，朗拿根在對[[李斯特城足球會|李斯特城]]的賽事中，於己方禁區的遠射得手<ref>{{en}}[http://www.skysports.com/football/match_report/0,19764,11065_2390987,00.html Match Report | Leicester v Preston NE - 2nd October 2004 | Sky Sports | Football News<!-- Bot generated title -->]{{dead link|date=六月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

2004/05球季，朗拿根受到新領隊[[比利·戴維斯|戴維斯]]的重視，出戰聯賽大半部分的賽事，後來由於他的傷患問題，球會從[[米杜士堡足球會|米杜士堡]]引入門將[[卡路·拿殊|拿殊]]，而在2005年初於訓練期間受傷的朗拿根，在2005年末才康復並被外借至[[韋甘比足球會|韋甘比]]<ref>{{en}}[http://www.wycombewanderers.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10430~21722,00.html Wycombe Wanderers | Team | First Team | Andy Lonergan<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wycombewanderers.co.uk/page/ProfilesDetail/0,,10430~21722,00.html |date=20120607074346 }}</ref>。

2006年11月，朗拿根被外借至[[史雲頓足球會|史雲頓]]，為期一個月。然而，由於並未受到剛取代[[丹尼斯·韋斯|韋斯]]擔任領隊的{{Link-en|保罗·斯特罗克|Paul Sturrock|斯特罗克}}的重用，因此他提早歸隊。

2007年1月，由於拿殊不專業的態度，意味著朗拿根得以再次上陣，出戰以2-0的比分擊敗[[水晶宮足球會|水晶宮]]的[[英格蘭足總盃|足總盃]]賽事。他亦從而確立自己的正選地位，並且贏得2008/09球季普雷斯頓年度最佳球員<ref name=autogenerated8 />。

2009年8月，時任普雷斯頓隊{{Link-en|保罗·麦肯纳|Paul McKenna (footballer)|麦肯纳}}被出售至[[諾定咸森林足球會|諾定咸森林]]後，朗拿根被任命為副隊長。9月12日，他在以2-0的比分擊敗[[史雲斯足球會|史雲斯]]的賽事中首次以隊長的身份上陣。時任領隊[[阿兰·埃尔文|埃尔文]]聲稱他的表現足夠代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭]]上陣<ref name=autogenerated5>{{en}}[http://www.football.co.uk/preston_north_end/irvine_lauds_lonergan_potential_rss246512.shtml Irvine lauds Lonergan potential - Preston North End News from football.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.football.co.uk/preston_north_end/irvine_lauds_lonergan_potential_rss246512.shtml |date=20121006205535 }}</ref>。

2009/10球季，朗拿根再次贏得球會年度最佳球員<ref>{{en}}[http://www.pnefc.net/page/ProfilesDetail Preston North End | Team | Profiles | Andy Lonergan<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pnefc.net/page/ProfilesDetail |date=20120712010745 }}</ref><ref name=autogenerated7 />。在球季末段，他在普雷斯頓以6-0的比分擊敗[[卡迪夫城足球會|卡迪夫城]]的賽事中救出[[十二碼|十二碼]]，協助球會壓過對方取得附加賽資格<ref>{{en}}[http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/apr/18/league-round-up-preston-north-end-cardiff-city Football League round-up: Mellor strikes signal rout as Preston hit six | Football | The Observer<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/football/2009/apr/18/league-round-up-preston-north-end-cardiff-city |date=20090421054546 }}</ref>，然而最終不敵[[錫菲聯足球會|錫菲聯]]<ref>{{en}}[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8040418.stm BBC SPORT | Football | Friday football as it happened<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/8040418.stm |date=20090511131808 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.djmick.co.uk/sport/football/playoffs-sheffield-united-1-preston-0/ |title=Playoffs: Sheffield United 1 Preston 0 {{!}} djmick: V2<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2011-08-05 |archive-date=2011-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110916071226/http://www.djmick.co.uk/sport/football/playoffs-sheffield-united-1-preston-0/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。其後，英超球會西布朗連續對他出價三次被拒後，時任普雷斯頓領隊[[戴倫·費格遜|費格遜]]稱朗拿根價值2000萬英鎊，而且是非賣品<ref>{{en}}[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6272005,00.html PNE snub new Lonergan bid | Football News | Sky Sports<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_6272005,00.html |date=20150924140958 }}</ref>。

2010/11球季，朗拿根代表普雷斯頓在[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]上陣29次。2010年9月，他被控告在以3-4的比分不敵[[般尼足球會|般尼]]的賽事中，向對方球迷作猥褻姿勢<ref>{{en}}[http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/8389638.No_action_over_Lonergan_gestures_to_Burnley_crowd/ No action over Lonergan gestures to Burnley crowd (From Lancashire Telegraph)<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.lancashiretelegraph.co.uk/sport/8389638.No_action_over_Lonergan_gestures_to_Burnley_crowd/ |date=20160820125306 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}[http://www.football.co.uk/preston_north_end/players/andy_lonergan_52294.shtml Andy Lonergan - Preston North End Football Club<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.football.co.uk/preston_north_end/players/andy_lonergan_52294.shtml |date=20120222062125 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8977578.stm BBC Sport - Football - Burnley 4-3 Preston<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref><ref>{{en}}[http://www.offthepost.info/2010/09/preston-goalie-andy-lonergan-in-trouble-over-v-signs-towards-burnley-fans/ Preston goalie Andy Lonergan in trouble over V-signs towards Burnley fans »<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.offthepost.info/2010/09/preston-goalie-andy-lonergan-in-trouble-over-v-signs-towards-burnley-fans/ |date=20100925044859 }}</ref>，他最終被罰款並遭到警告<ref>{{en}}[http://www.football.co.uk/burnley/pne_s_lonergan_hit_with_fa_fine_rss1295595.shtml PNE's Lonergan hit with FA fine - Burnley News from football.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.football.co.uk/burnley/pne_s_lonergan_hit_with_fa_fine_rss1295595.shtml |date=20121006210042 }}</ref>。同月，他在以6-4的比分擊敗[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]的賽事中上陣，球會在落後1-4的情況下連入5球，反敗為勝<ref>{{en}}[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/9031722.stm BBC Sport - Football - Leeds 4-6 Preston<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/9031722.stm |date=20191219002707 }}</ref>。1月轉會市場開啟後，他與[[曼城足球會|曼城]]和[[韋根足球會|韋根]]扯上關係<ref>{{en}}[http://www.people.co.uk/sport/fo