ton goalkeeper Andy Lonergan<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>。另外，他一度與黑池扯上關係，以緊急借用的形式代替受傷的[[保罗·拉楚布卡|拉楚布卡]]和[[李察·京遜|京遜]]<ref>{{en}}[http://www.people.co.uk/sport/football/football-hotline/2011/02/20/ian-holloway-chases-andy-lonergan-on-loan-to-provide-cover-at-blackpool-102039-22934858/ Ian Holloway chases Andy Lonergan on loan to provide cover at Blackpool - Football Hotline - Football - Sport - People.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.people.co.uk/sport/football/football-hotline/2011/02/20/ian-holloway-chases-andy-lonergan-on-loan-to-provide-cover-at-blackpool-102039-22934858/ |date=20120330083634 }}</ref>。2011年3月8日，他在以1-2的比分不敵列斯聯的賽事中最後一次代表普雷斯頓上陣<ref name=autogenerated6>{{en}}[http://www.pnefc.net/page/NewsDetail/0,,10362~2401416,00.html Preston North End | News | Latest | Latest | Lonergan Departs Deepdale<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.pnefc.net/page/NewsDetail/0,,10362~2401416,00.html |date=20120911003251 }}</ref>。球會降班後，他與[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]<ref>{{en}}[http://thesun.mobi/sol/homepage/sport/football/3655716/Villa-eye-Prestons-Lonergan.html?mob=1 Eck hopes Lone deal is for keeps - The Sun mobile<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>、卡迪夫城<ref>{{en}}[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_6713893,00.html Preston reject bids for trio | Sky Sports | Football | Championship | News<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_6713893,00.html |date=20160815102643 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}[http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Everton-transfer-news-Cardiff-are-trying-to-hijack-Preston-keeper-Andy-Lonergan-proposed-move-to-Goodison-Park-article709606.html Everton transfer news Cardiff are trying to hijack Preston keeper Andy Lonergan proposed move to Goodison Park - News - MirrorFootball.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Everton-transfer-news-Cardiff-are-trying-to-hijack-Preston-keeper-Andy-Lonergan-proposed-move-to-Goodison-Park-article709606.html |date=20121016070822 }}</ref>和愛華頓扯上關係<ref>{{en}}[http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Everton-transfer-news-Preston-keeper-Andy-Lonergan-to-join-for-750k-but-cannot-play-until-next-season-article693887.html Everton transfer news Preston keeper Andy Lonergan to join for £750k but cannot play until next season - News - MirrorFootball.co.uk<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mirrorfootball.co.uk/news/Everton-transfer-news-Preston-keeper-Andy-Lonergan-to-join-for-750k-but-cannot-play-until-next-season-article693887.html |date=20110829214535 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}[http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2011447/Spurs-face-Giuseppe-Rossi-battle-Leeds-land-Lonergan--THE-INSIDER.html Spurs face Giuseppe Rossi battle, Leeds land Lonergan - THE INSIDER | Mail Online<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-2011447/Spurs-face-Giuseppe-Rossi-battle-Leeds-land-Lonergan--THE-INSIDER.html |date=20160918051941 }}</ref>。時任領隊菲爾·布朗稱，他需要出售朗拿根以填補買入伊恩·端納的費用<ref>{{en}}[http://www.dailypost.co.uk/sport-news/everton-fc/2011/06/23/everton-fc-eyeing-preston-keeper-andy-lonergan-55578-28926553/ Everton FC eyeing Preston keeper Andy Lonergan - Everton FC - Sport News - Daily Post North Wales<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dailypost.co.uk/sport-news/everton-fc/2011/06/23/everton-fc-eyeing-preston-keeper-andy-lonergan-55578-28926553/ |date=20120929170628 }}</ref>。

2011年7月4日，朗拿根與有兩位門將[[卡斯柏·舒米高|舒米高]]和[[沙恩·希捷士|希捷士]]離隊的列斯聯扯上關係<ref>{{en}}[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_7020912,00.html Lonergan on Leeds radar | Sky Sports | Football | Championship | News<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_7020912,00.html |date=20121023172154 }}</ref>，與此同時愛華頓也對他有興趣<ref>{{en}}[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11671_7028072,00.html Everton enter Lonergan chase | Everton News, Fixtures, Results, Transfers | Sky Sports<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11671_7028072,00.html |date=20160305015507 }}</ref>。

其後，球會確認朗拿根有意加盟列斯聯。本來，列斯聯對[[大卫·斯托克戴尔|斯托克戴尔]]有興趣，而朗拿根則有興趣加盟愛華頓，加上他的女兒當時正在留醫，這些都一度使這宗轉會暫緩下來<ref>{{en}}[http://www.leeds.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=248518 Leeds - LUFC Lonergan - It was never a matter of finance<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.leeds.vitalfootball.co.uk/article.asp?a=248518 |date=20110810021253 }}</ref><ref>{{en}}[http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_7060534,00.html Leeds to land Lonergan | Sky Sports | Football | Championship | News<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11688_7060534,00.html |date=20160308035055 }}</ref>。

===列斯聯===
7月25日，朗拿根正式轉投列斯聯，並簽訂三年合約<ref name=autogenerated1 />。他將會與[[保罗·拉楚布卡|拉楚布卡]]競逐舒米高留下的正選門將席位<ref name=autogenerated6 /><ref>{{en}}[http://www.football365.com/championship/7061466/ Lonergan signs up for Leeds | Football365 | Championship News<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.football365.com/championship/7061466/ |date=20120327145749 }}</ref>。與此同時，他與曾任黑池領隊的[[西蒙·加利臣|加利臣]]故劍重逢<ref name=autogenerated4 />。他在季前熱身賽對[[紐卡素足球會|紐卡素]]的賽事中首次代表列斯聯上陣<ref>{{en}}http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20110731/paynter-goal-secures-victory_2247585_2406373 {{Wayback|url=http://www.leedsunited.com/news/20110731/paynter-goal-secures-victory_2247585_2406373 |date=20120929235838 }}</ref>。

===保頓===
2012年7月17日，朗拿根加盟剛降班到[[英冠|英冠]]的[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]，簽訂三年合約，轉會金額無透露。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bwfc.co.uk/page/General/0,,1004~2851466,00.html |title=Wanderers Recruit Lonergan |publisher=bwfc.co.uk |date=17 July 2012 |accessdate=18 July 2012 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120719224012/http://www.bwfc.co.uk/page/General/0%2C%2C1004~2851466%2C00.html |archivedate=2012-07-19 }}</ref>

==國家隊==
曾經代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭U16]]上陣一次的朗拿根決定改為代表他的出生地[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]<ref name=autogenerated2 />。他是前英格蘭U21國腳<ref>{{en}}[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/england/3487231.stm BBC SPORT | Football | Internationals | England | Stead gets Under-21 call<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/england/3487231.stm |date=20040325225436 }}</ref>。他亦曾經代表英格蘭U20出戰U20世界盃<ref name=autogenerated5 />。由於他的祖父母是愛爾蘭人，所以他合資格代表[[愛爾蘭國家足球隊|愛爾蘭]]上陣<ref name=autogenerated3 />。2010年5月，最初他拒絕被愛爾蘭徵召後，後來他才願意<ref>{{en}}[http://www.footballfancast.com/2010/05/football-blogs/lonergan-would-welcome-ireland-call-up Lonergan would welcome Ireland call up | FootballFanCast.com<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.footballfancast.com/2010/05/football-blogs/lonergan-would-welcome-ireland-call-up |date=20120313060019 }}</ref>。2011年，[[沙伊·吉文|吉文]]由於傷患缺陣一段時間，因而產生朗拿根被徵召的可能性<ref>{{en}}[http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/sport/2011/0224/1224290733718.html Given likely to be out for three months - The Irish Times - Thu, Feb 24, 2011<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{Wayback|url=http://www.irishtimes.com/newspaper/sport/2011/0224/1224290733718.html |date=20110224040407 }}</ref>。

